.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
4 different games are played: poker, canasta, chess, mah-jongg
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, horror, mystery, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, trance
1. the person playing poker is the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
4. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
5. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is the person playing chess##1
7. the fan of funk is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
8. the person playing mah-jongg is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Game           | canasta | chess | mah-jongg | poker |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | mystery  | horror | disaster   |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | folk     | reggae | funk       |

