1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the spanish is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the person traveling to marseilles is the pakistani##1
7. the spanish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| City         | colone   | venice   | marseilles | hamburg |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure | disaster   | mystery |
| Nationality   | spanish     | canadian  | pakistani  | german  |

