4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person watching sports movies is the person drinking water##1
6. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
7. the person drinking coffee is the person watching comedy movies##1
8. the person watching romance movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |    3     |    4     |
