4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the mexican is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |    4    |
