House: wooden, cape-cod, cottage, farmhouse
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
2. the wooden house is on the right of the nurse##1
3. the lawyer is on the right of the nurse##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the chef##1
5. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the accountant##1
7. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the cottage house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2   |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby       | cape-codd-games | chess | writing | woodworking |
| Job         | accountant | chef  | nurse   | lawyer      |
| House   | cape-cod        | cottage  | farmhouse   | wooden         |

